msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 9 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 9 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an9.30:0.2"
msgid "3. Sattāvāsavagga "
msgstr "3. Abodes of Sentient Beings "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an9.30:0.3"
msgid "30. Āghātapaṭivinayasutta "
msgstr "30. Getting Rid of Resentment "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.409, sc1
msgctxt "an9.30:1.1"
msgid "“Navayime, bhikkhave, āghātapaṭivinayā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these nine methods to get rid of resentment. "

msgctxt "an9.30:1.2"
msgid "Katame nava? "
msgstr "What nine? "

#. VAR: acari → acarīti (s1-3)
msgctxt "an9.30:1.3"
msgid "‘Anatthaṃ me acari, taṃ kutettha labbhā’ti āghātaṃ paṭivineti; "
msgstr "Thinking: ‘They harmed me, but what can I possibly do?’ you get rid of resentment. "

msgctxt "an9.30:1.4"
msgid "‘anatthaṃ me carati, taṃ kutettha labbhā’ti āghātaṃ paṭivineti; "
msgstr "Thinking: ‘They are harming me …’ … "

msgctxt "an9.30:1.5"
msgid "‘anatthaṃ me carissati, taṃ kutettha labbhā’ti āghātaṃ paṭivineti; "
msgstr "‘They will harm me …’ … "

msgctxt "an9.30:1.6"
msgid "piyassa me manāpassa anatthaṃ acari … pe … "
msgstr "‘They harmed someone I love …’ … "

msgctxt "an9.30:1.7"
msgid "anatthaṃ carati … pe … "
msgstr "‘They are harming someone I love …’ "

msgctxt "an9.30:1.8"
msgid "‘anatthaṃ carissati, taṃ kutettha labbhā’ti āghātaṃ paṭivineti; "
msgstr "‘They will harm someone I love …’ … "

msgctxt "an9.30:1.9"
msgid "appiyassa me amanāpassa atthaṃ acari … pe … "
msgstr "‘They helped someone I dislike …’ … "

msgctxt "an9.30:1.10"
msgid "atthaṃ carati … pe … "
msgstr "‘They are helping someone I dislike …’ … "

msgctxt "an9.30:1.11"
msgid "‘atthaṃ carissati, taṃ kutettha labbhā’ti āghātaṃ paṭivineti. "
msgstr "Thinking: ‘They will help someone I dislike, but what can I possibly do?’ you get rid of resentment. "

msgctxt "an9.30:1.12"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, nava āghātapaṭivinayā”ti. "
msgstr "These are the nine methods to get rid of resentment.” "

